Interface GeoHashGrid

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Aggregation, MultiBucketsAggregation
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    InternalGeoHashGrid

    public interface GeoHashGrid
extends MultiBucketsAggregation
    A geohash_grid aggregation. Defines multiple buckets, each representing a cell in a geo-grid of a specific precision.
